title: La Comunidad- DVD-RIP
description: Julia finds 300 million pesetas hidden in a dead man&#039;s house while selling an apartment. She&#039;s a 40-ish real estate agent (played by Carmen Maura) now forced to face the wrath of a very peculiar community (of neighbors), headed by an unscrupulous administrator.
